<dl id="n09049c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n09" href="#n09049c">N09 (VI.B.1)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n09all.htm#n09049c"> 49(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> threatened her with bloodshed</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><b>Items from Far and Near &hellip; Boy&apos;s &ldquo;Bloodshed&rdquo; Threat</b>. For sending a letter to a school superintendent <mark>threatening her with bloodshed</mark> and demanding &pound;5, a boy of 13 was, at Lyeland, Lancashire, sent to a reformatory school for five years. <small> <a name="FJ25feb24" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FJ25feb24"><cite title="source">Freeman's Journal</cite></a> (25 February 1924) 7/2</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
